  "text": "Hi, I am Tom. I go to the supermarket every Saturday. I always buy a lot of food. I buy six apples and ten eggs. I buy some milk and some cheese. I have a big bag for my food. The apples are cheap, but the cheese is expensive. I do not have a lot of money, so I buy only what I need.",
